From: Joel Fernandes <joelagnelf@nvidia.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Oct 2025 11:13:21 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] gpu: nova-core: bitfield: Move bitfield-specific code from
 register! into new macro
References: bsc#1258210
Patch-mainline: 6.18.33
Git-commit: 71ea85be25b4f54a53ec03d5deaed52f5ee65da8

[ Upstream commit 71ea85be25b4f54a53ec03d5deaed52f5ee65da8 ]

Move the bitfield-specific code from the register macro into a new macro
called bitfield. This will be used to define structs with bitfields,
similar to C language.

